      "content": {
        "title": "Paediatric Sports and Overuse Injuries — Core Principles",
        "definition": "Apophysitis, stress fractures, and osteochondritis dissecans in skeletally immature athletes including Little Leaguer elbow.",
        "summary": "Osgood-Schlatter and Sever disease are traction apophysitis. Little Leaguer elbow involves medial epicondyle apophysitis. OCD may need drilling or fixation."
      },
